      <div class="msgContentFrame">With the lack of content available in the game, why not let players at least grind  regional levequests for character progression? If you have to, reduce the gold/item rewards. <br /> <br />I think the lockout would have been fine, if there was anything else to do in this game while leveling up class ranks... But there's not. <br /> <br />Adding more leves in the upcoming patches isn't going to be enough if we can only do 8 every 36 hours. There needs to be more leves available (which SE is working on), and the game shouldn't be so restrictive on how many we can take on.</div>
